      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Well, Java serialization and deserialization into binary stream is not what the question is about, anyway. So it is only good that Jackson offers multiple patterns to be used with deserialization. I especially like the builder pattern as it allows the resulting object to be immutable."
