    "question_id" : 7625783,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You have to create dummy empty constructor in our model class.So while mapping json, it set by setter method.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 151394,
      "reputation" : 53743,
      "user_id" : 365237,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 96,
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/fb9385b7f1a792d5159eca8bbb2c34f8?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "eis",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/365237/eis"
