    "last_activity_date" : 1528488439,
    "creation_date" : 1528488439,
    "answer_id" : 50767748,
    "question_id" : 7625783,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>For me, this used to work, but upgrading libraries caused this issue to appear. Problem was having a class like this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>package example.counter;\n\nimport javax.validation.constraints.NotNull;\n\nimport lombok.Data;\n\n@Data\npublic class CounterRequest {\n    @NotNull\n    private final Integer int1;\n\n    @NotNull\n    private final Integer int2;\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Using lombok:</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;dependency&gt;\n    &lt;groupId&gt;org.projectlombok&lt;/groupId&gt;\n    &lt;artifactId&gt;lombok&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n    &lt;version&gt;1.18.0&lt;/version&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Falling back to</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;dependency&gt;\n    &lt;groupId&gt;org.projectlombok&lt;/groupId&gt;\n    &lt;artifactId&gt;lombok&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n    &lt;version&gt;1.16.10&lt;/version&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Fixed the issue. Not sure why, but wanted to document it for future.</p>\n"
  }, {
